the game is played with two players. P1 (green) uses "aswd" and p2 (blue) uses arrow keys for movement.
the aim is to fill most area with their respective colour.
there are difernt obstacles like pitfalls and opposite player that attacks you. 
the game starts with 100 second timer and 3 lives for each player.
if the player falls down the pit or go out of boundary, a life is lost.
also the paintmeter gets finished after a certain limit. to refill you have to go to the startng point.
There are additional collectibles like extra life and paint refill power ups which spawn every five seconds and disaapears after 10 seconds.
The player to fill max amount in gven time wins
if the player lose all its lives, the opponent automatically wins.
